# Employee Directory – Frontend UI Assignment

This project is a **responsive and interactive employee directory web interface** built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript**, and **Freemarker templates**. It is part of a frontend assignment to demonstrate modular design, clean UI, and client-side functionality.

---

##  Features

- Dashboard with list/grid view of employees
- Search by name or email
- Filter by First Name, Department, Role
- Add/Edit employee form with validation
- Edit and Delete actions per employee
- Pagination (basic setup)
- Responsive design for mobile/tablet/desktop
- Uses Freemarker for dynamic rendering
- No backend required — mock data in Freemarker & JS

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (vanilla)
- JavaScript (vanilla)
- Freemarker Template Engine

